@addictedtofauna3838Kim didn’t neglect him, she just didn’t tolerate his disrespect, rebellion, and rambunctious behavior. 

She favored Yoon because he actually deserved it: he was respectful, eager to learn, a great fighter, and did what he was asked. 

She raised Kwon the only way she knew how. She clearly didn’t know how to deal with his natural temperament, but she still clearly kept him fed, clothes, and sheltered, despite his disrespect.
